</P>
<P>
One Youth Wounded 
</P>
<P>
The youths, whose names were not released, sped off but drove into a dead end 
and had to turn around and drive back past Poe's home, according to the 
Sheriff's Department. Poe's neighbor, Faulkner, whose home had been burglarized 
recently, fired a shot at the car as it drove off, deputies said. 
</P>
<P>
